Holala buried barrel near Leaning
Tower of Dorrick in Temperantia.

rows.label: qst201918_msg0002
rows.name:
Surely friends not go and
dig up barrel after Holala
go to trouble of burying?

rows.label: qst201918_msg0003
rows.name:
Holala not happy about that... But
also not want to meet same fate as
Suisui, so Holala not argue.
